===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
[[File:Masters Trials on the Isle.png|thumb|left|250px|Selene and {{mas|Elio}} in the [[Trials on the Isle]] [[story event]] banner]]
{{main|Selene (Masters)}}
Selene, in her {{g|Sun and Moon}} design, forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Rowlet}} and its evolved forms {{p|Dartrix}} and {{p|Decidueye}}, along with {{p|Umbreon}}, {{p|Scizor}}, {{p|Nihilego}}, and {{Shiny}} {{form|Necrozma|Dawn Wings}} {{p|Necrozma}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Her Scizor is capable of [[Mega Evolution|Mega Evolving]]. Selene became a playable sync pair on April 15, 2021.

Selene has also made notable appearances in one of the game's main stories, the [[villain arc]]. Unlike in the original games, both Selene and {{mas|Elio}} coexist in this game.

